DESCRIPTION:
Pushing the boundaries of what fans can expect from the record-breaking entertainment franchise, Call Of Duty: Black Ops II propels players into the near future of the 21st century, the Cold War, where technology and weapons have converged to create a new generation of war! Call of Duty: Black Ops II - multi-platform video game in the genre of three-dimensional first-person shooter. Is the ninth game in the Call of Duty series and the direct sequel to Call of Duty: Black Ops. Developed by American studio Treyarch. The official announcement of the game - May 1, 2012.
In the single-player campaign action takes place in two time frames - in the near future (the main action game that was originally planned when creating the game), and at the time of the first Cold War. The campaign will provide answers to questions left open after the Call of Duty: Black Ops: Is Alex Mason killed Kennedy or someone else did it? How to survive Frank Woods? Who really Victor Reznov.
